CUSTOMER.AGE: Function DerivedValue(xmlNode) DerivedValue = "" If Not xmlNode.attributes.getNamedItem("DATEOFBIRTH") Is Nothing Then dtDob = CDate(xmlNode.attributes.getNamedItem("DATEOFBIRTH").Text) nDoB = (Year(dtDob) * 10000) + (Month(dtDob) * 100) + Day(dtDob) nNow = (Year(Now) * 10000) + (Month(Now) * 100) + Day(Now) DerivedValue = Fix((nNow - nDoB) / 10000) End If End Function

Function DerivedValue(xmlNode) DerivedValue=""
If Not xmlNode.attributes.getNamedItem("DATEOFBIRTH") Is Nothing Then
dtDob=CDate(xmlNode.attributes.getNamedItem("DATEOFBIRTH").Text)
nDoB=(Year(dtDob) * 10000) + (Month(dtDob) * 100) + Day(dtDob)
nNow=(Year(Now) * 10000) + (Month(Now) * 100) + Day(Now)
DerivedValue=Fix((nNow - nDoB) / 10000)
End If End Function
